content.data: This is a Drill and Dowel Machine Link.
Output for the T.O.P Drill & Dowel machine.

When a Tool in the Tool Catalog is assigned to this machine you will 
 get the following Parameters:

Drill 
 (_hmDrill) 
	  Allows you to specify that this tool should perform a drill 
	 operation 
 Insert 
 (_hmInsert) 
	  Allows you to specify that this tool should perform an insertion 
	 operation 
 Macro 
 (_hmMacro) 
	 - Macro name to use for the insertion operation
